        ],
        "management": "Initiate quadruple GDMT: ARNI (sacubitril/valsartan 24/26mg BID, titrate to 97/103mg) + beta-blocker (carvedilol 3.125mg BID titrate to 25mg BID, or bisoprolol 1.25mg daily to 10mg) + MRA (spironolactone 12.5-25mg daily or eplerenone 25mg BID) + SGLT2i (dapagliflozin 10mg or empagliflozin 10mg). Loop diuretic for congestion. ICD if LVEF <=35% after 3mo GDMT. CRT if QRS >=150ms LBBB."
