          { "feature": "comorbidities_obesity_htn_dm_afib_elderly", "weight": 4 }
        ],
        "management": "Treat comorbidities (HTN, DM, obesity, AFib). SGLT2i (dapagliflozin/empagliflozin 10mg) reduces HF hospitalization. Diuretics for congestion. Consider ARNI in select patients (LVEF <60% or recent HF hospitalization). Avoid beta-blocker as first line unless specific indication. Exercise training and weight loss highly effective."
      },
